# update.json is machine-written by scripts/release.mjs with LF endings on
# every release; declare that canonical so git on Windows (autocrlf) neither
# converts it nor warns "LF will be replaced by CRLF" during the release flow.
# This file declares itself LF too, for the same reason.
/.gitattributes text eol=lf
/update.json text eol=lf
